      /* root */
      :root {
        --w-1: 100%;
        --w-2: 50%;
        --w-3: 33.3333333%;
        --w-4: 25%;
        --w-5: 20%;
        --w-6: 16.66666%;
        
        /* Color */
        --grey: $(color.root.grey);
        --grey-dark: $(color.root.grey.dark);
        --red: $(color.root.red);
        --red-dark: $(color.root.red.dark);
        --yellow-dark: $(color.root.yellow.dark);
        --black: $(color.root.black);
      }
      /* Riset Css*/
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-box-sizing: border-box;-moz-box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-word}
      * {margin:0;padding:0;font:inherit}
      img,
      picture,
      svg,
      video {max-width: 100%;}
      .none,.hidden {display: none}
      input {outline: none}
      .separator{pointer-events:none}
    
    
      
    
    
      
    
    
      
    
    
      
    

    
      
        /*------Layout (No Edit)----------*/
        body#layout #outer-wrapper,body#layout .row{width:auto;padding:0}
        body#layout{max-width:860px;position:relative;padding:95px 5px 5px;margin:0 auto}
        body#layout div.section{margin:0 5px 10px!important;padding:16px 16px 18px!important}
        body#layout .section h4{font-size:14px;margin:0}
        body#layout::before {content: "AnimeParadise Beta v1.0.2";font-family: sans-serif;padding: 10px 20px;font-size: 18px;border: 1px solid #d6d6d6;border-radius: 10px;background: linear-gradient(to right,#80828e,#2f79c5);font-weight: 700;color: #fff;}
        body#layout:after {content: " Desain By Yukine ";padding: 10px;font-size: 20px;visibility: visible;}
        body#layout .visibility {min-height: 0;}
        body#layout .layout-widget-description {display: none;}
        body#layout .locked-widget .widget-wrap3 {padding-left: 10px;background: #2e79c5;}
        body#layout .locked-widget .visibility .layout-widget-state.visible {background-image: url("https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-qicweZaCb7I/XR_IGBqqGfI/AAAAAAAABS0/MIpI_COKj6MBkeN9FEJhqL96WYnYfGjngCK4BGAYYCw/s1600/visibility_c3_600_24dp.png") !important;}
        body#layout .visibility .editlink {background: #3c97ef url("https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-iQoCOwqjB-w/Wy1bDznOM4I/AAAAAAAACGA/8BUOPStr0sk5oud9hWpHBQTrmkeJDoAvACK4BGAYYCw/s18-c/mode_edit_w600_24dp.png") no-repeat center !important;}
        body#layout .draggable-widget .visibility .editlink {background: #757575 url("https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-iQoCOwqjB-w/Wy1bDznOM4I/AAAAAAAACGA/8BUOPStr0sk5oud9hWpHBQTrmkeJDoAvACK4BGAYYCw/s18-c/mode_edit_w600_24dp.png") no-repeat center !important;}
        body#layout .header-mobile {width: 320px;}
        body#layout div#berkas-search {width: 223px;}
        body#layout .menu-bk {padding: 0px;}
        body#layout footer {padding: 0;}
        body#layout .konten-berkas {padding-top: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;position: relative;}
        body#layout .konten-berkas::after {content: '!!Masih Belum Support All Widget!!';position: absolute;top: 0;font-size: 30px;left: 0;right: 0;color: red;font-family: 'Roboto';}
        body#layout .konten-berkas::before {content: ' Kode Lisensi ';position: absolute;bottom: 10px;font-size: 30px;left: 5px;right: 5px;color: #2f79c5;font-family: 'Roboto';font-weight: bold;border: 2px solid;}

        /* visibility */
        body#layout .visibility .layout-widget-state.not-visible {background-image: url(https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-d0aG6MhB1wE/Ykzc3T4Pg4I/AAAAAAAAABk/7YlG6z_NIicCTJsfvw9U5Aka0aTe_7dMwCNcBGAsYHQ/s24/visibility_off_red_24dp.png) !important;opacity: 1;}

        body#layout #license>h4:after {content: ' - https://rasgane.com/';font-size: 12px;font-weight: 400;color: red;}
